beer.beer_description: Dad & Dave’s #1 Pale Ale is a simple full flavoured beer derived from 100% Australian malted barley. Hops grown in Nelson, New Zealand impart “fruitiness” typical of Sauvignon Blanc grape varieties with passionfruit aromas with a crisp finish. English Ale yeast is also used to bring out the natural sweetness of the malt and hops.
